Class LimitedTellerMachineTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • teller.LimitedTellerMachineTest
  • public class LimitedTellerMachineTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Test class for the LimitedTellerMachine. This class contains unit tests to verify the functionality of depositing and withdrawing money.
